</md></sn><sn><md>### Altitude{.text-center}

:::.row
:::.col-12 .col-lg-7
* Places at sea level record higher temperatures than those at higher elevations.
* Temperature usually decreases with increasing height.
* The rate of decrease of temperature with height is called the ++normal lapse rate++.
:::

